Package: investoSim
Title: Simulate Basic Investment Strategies
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jaxson", "Pham", email = "jaxsonpham@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight R package to simulate and compare basic investment strategies 
    such as lump-sum investing and dollar-cost averaging (DCA). The goal of this package 
    is to help beginner investors, students, or educators visualize how different 
    approaches to investing can impact long-term portfolio value. Built for educational 
    purposes and simple experimentation.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr
License: CC0
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/jaxsonpham/investoSim
BugReports: https://github.com/jaxsonpham/investoSim/issues
